%% Sequence 2 - Use case: View scan history
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant UI as Browser page
    participant API as FastAPI route
    participant DEP as get_db dependency
    participant RP as ScanRepository
    participant DB as Database

    U->>UI: open the scanner page
    UI->>API: GET /scans + X-Session-Id
    API->>DEP: request a session
    DEP-->>API: Session
    API->>API: current_session(header)
    API->>RP: ScanRepository(db, session_id).list(50)
    RP->>DB: SELECT * FROM scans WHERE session_id = ? ORDER BY created_at DESC
    DB-->>RP: rows
    RP-->>API: list of Scan entities
    API-->>UI: 200 OK, list of ScanOut
    UI->>UI: build history table
    UI-->>U: recent scans displayed
    API->>DEP: close session
